headline.main: Murray Survives Seven Match Points in Dubai Quarterfinals
headline.print_headline: Murray Survives Seven Match Points in Dubai Quarterfinals

lead_paragraph: Morgan Stanley economists said on Thursday they expected the Federal Reserve will raise U.S. interest rates by a quarter point to a range of 0.75-1.00 percent at its upcoming policy meeting in less than two weeks.
